com.fluidops.iwb.autocompletion
Class AutoCompleteFactory

java.lang.Object
  com.fluidops.iwb.autocompletion.AutoCompleteFactory

public class AutoCompleteFactory
extends java.lang.Object

Factory class to produce auto suggestion objects, which implement AutoSuggesters. The produced objects generate auto suggestions for various kinds of free text input, typically used with FComponents, e.g., for auto suggestions in text search or triple input.

Author:
cp, Sebastian Godelet
